Parliament of Uganda on 7 February 2012. Reportedly, there are several grave 
human rights concerns regarding the contents of the Bill. These include the 
imposition of the death penalty for &#8222;aggravated homosexuality&#8223;, including for &#8222;serial 
</p>
<p>offenders&#8223; and those who are living with HIV; the criminalization of the &#8222;promotion 
</p>
