Internet, films, mobile phones for &#8222;purposes of homosexuality or promoting 
</p>
<p>homosexuality&#8223;; and the criminalization of the failure to report to the authorities 
</p>
<p>those people who citizens suspect of being homosexual. The proposed legislation 
may arbitrarily discriminate against LGBTI people and associations advocating for 
human rights without discrimination. 
