<p><b>Torture;  Violence 
</b></p>
<p><b>against women;   
</b></p>
<p> 
</p>
<p>Alleged rape of an 18-year-old girl by her stepfather, a police officer, for more than 
five years. According to the information received, Ms. X (18), a resident in Punjab 
Province was continuously raped for five years by her stepfather, a police officer of 
the area. The victim also stated that she was forced to have three abortions. She also 
reported that she had been threatened by the perpetrator not to talk about the matter 
with anyone, and that when she reported the facts to the police station, she was 
threatened not to file a complaint. It is finally reported that the mother of the victim 
has been disappeared for the last 10 months and her whereabouts remain unknown. 
